---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="About - AI Tools Reviews" description="Learn about our mission to provide independent, honest AI tool reviews">
  <Nav />
  
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-invert prose-slate">
    <h1>About AI Tools Reviews</h1>
    
    <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-300">
      We're on a mission to help you navigate the rapidly evolving world of AI tools with honest, in-depth reviews and real-world testing.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    
    <p>
      The AI tools landscape changes almost daily. New products launch, existing ones get major updates, and pricing models shift constantly. 
      It's overwhelming to keep up, let alone make informed decisions about which tools are worth your time and money.
    </p>

    <p>
      That's where we come in. We test every tool extensively, benchmark performance across real use cases, and provide honest assessments 
      of what works, what doesn't, and who each tool is actually best for.
    </p>

    <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>Hands-on testing</strong> - We actually use these tools for weeks, not just read the marketing materials</li>
      <li><strong>Real benchmarks</strong> - Data-driven comparisons across multiple dimensions</li>
      <li><strong>Honest critiques</strong> - We call out limitations and overpriced features</li>
      <li><strong>Regular updates</strong> - AI tools evolve fast; we keep our reviews current</li>
      <li><strong>No BS</strong> - Clear verdicts on who should buy and who should skip</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Our Testing Process</h2>

    <p>
      For each tool, we spend 2-4 weeks testing across various scenarios. We measure performance quantitatively where possible, 
      compare against alternatives, and evaluate real-world value for different user types.
    </p>

    <p>
      Our reviews include performance benchmarks, pricing analysis, feature comparisons, and honest assessments of strengths and weaknesses.
    </p>

    <h2>Transparency & Affiliate Links</h2>

    <p>
      We're committed to complete transparency. This site uses affiliate links, which means we may earn a commission if you purchase 
      a tool through our links. This comes at no extra cost to you.
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong>Important:</strong> Affiliate relationships do not influence our reviews. We maintain editorial independence and provide 
      honest assessments regardless of commission rates. Some of our most critical reviews are of tools with the best affiliate programs.
    </p>

    <p>
      If a tool is overpriced, buggy, or not worth it, we'll say soâ€”even if it means losing potential commissions.
    </p>

    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>

    <p>
      Have a tool you'd like us to review? Questions about our testing methodology? Want to discuss a potential partnership?
    </p>

    <p>
      <a href="/contact" class="text-brand hover:underline">Contact us</a> - we'd love to hear from you.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl not-prose">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Subscribe to Our Newsletter</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">Get weekly reviews, comparisons, and AI tool recommendations delivered to your inbox.</p>
      <form 
        action="https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_FORM_ID" 
        method="POST"
        class="flex gap-2 max-w-md"
      >
        <input 
          type="email" 
          name="email"
          placeholder="your@email.com" 
          required
          class="flex-1 px-4 py-2 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded focus:outline-none focus:border-brand"
        />
        <button 
          type="submit"
          class="px-6 py-2 bg-brand hover:bg-brand/80 rounded font-semibold transition-colors"
        >
          Subscribe
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose {
    @apply text-slate-300 leading-relaxed;
  }
  .prose h1 {
    @apply text-4xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-6;
  }
  .prose h2 {
    @apply text-3xl font-bold text-slate-100 mt-12 mb-4 pb-3 border-b-2 border-slate-700;
  }
  .prose h3 {
    @apply text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-100 mt-8 mb-3;
  }
  .prose p {
    @apply mb-5 leading-7;
  }
  .prose ul {
    @apply my-5 ml-6 space-y-2;
  }
  .prose li {
    @apply mb-2 leading-7;
  }
  .prose strong {
    @apply text-slate-100 font-semibold;
  }
  .prose a {
    @apply text-brand hover:underline;
  }
  .lead {
    @apply text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8;
  }
</style>
